cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is about image matching using a deep neural network architecture. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the end-to-end training of the network, which suggests that it may belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper introduces new layer types and a U-topology, which could be relevant to the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper deals with image processing, which could also place it in the sub-category of cs.MM (Multimedia).
